```

## The expected behavior

No lint errors.

## More details

A simple repro (taken from the link above) is:

```javascript.jsx
function Foo({ component: Component }) {
	const memoized = useMemo(() => ({
		render: () => <Component />
	}), [Component]);

	return memoized.render();
